# [T2TRG](../wg/t2trg.html)

## Summary

The Thing-to-Thing Research Group (T2TRG) met to discuss the role of IETF IoT technologies in enabling AI agent interactions with IoT environments. The session focused on two primary themes: **Discovery** (how agents find other agents, services, and devices) and the **Device Interaction Stack** (how agents understand and control physical IoT devices). The meeting concluded with a broader, philosophical discussion on the architectural and systemic risks of relying on AI abstractions in machine-to-machine (M2M) communication.

